<td class="px-6 py-4">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed text-caption rounded-full font-label-md">Hoàn thành</span>
</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
<button class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">visibility</button>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors group">
<td class="px-6 py-4 font-label-md text-primary">PN2408002</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">14/08/2024</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md">Phương Nam</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-right font-medium">8,100,000đ</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed text-caption rounded-full font-label-md">Hoàn thành</span>
</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
<button class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">visibility</button>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors group">
<td class="px-6 py-4 font-label-md text-primary">PN2408003</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">14/08/2024</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md">Fahasa</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-right font-medium">4,200,000đ</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-tertiary-fixed text-on-tertiary-fixed-variant text-caption rounded-full font-label-md">Đang chờ</span>
</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
<button class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">edit</button>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors group">
<td class="px-6 py-4 font-label-md text-primary">PN2408004</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">12/08/2024</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md">NXB Kim Đồng</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-right font-medium">21,000,000đ</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed text-caption rounded-full font-label-md">Hoàn thành</span>
</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
<button class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">visibility</button>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors group">
<td class="px-6 py-4 font-label-md text-primary">PN2408005</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">10/08/2024</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md">NXB Trẻ</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-right font-medium">5,600,000đ</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-error-container text-on-error-container text-caption rounded-full font-label-md">Đã hủy</span>
</td>
<td class="px-6 py-4 text-right">
<button class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">info</button>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class="p-6 border-t border-outline-variant flex justify-between items-center text-on-surface-variant">
<div class="text-caption">Hiển thị 1-5 trên 24 phiếu nhập</div>
<div class="flex space-x-2">
<button class="p-1 border border-outline-variant rounded hover:bg-surface-variant disabled:opacity-30" disabled="">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_left</span>
</button>
<button class="p-1 border border-outline-variant rounded hover:bg-surface-variant">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">chevron_right</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Secondary visual aid: Inventory Alert -->
<div class="bg-primary-container p-6 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant flex items-center space-x-6 text-on-primary-container">
<div class="h-24 w-24 rounded-lg overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
<img class="h-full w-full object-cover grayscale opacity-50 contrast-125" data-alt="A collection of vintage books stacked neatly in a warm, low-lit library setting. The focus is on the textures of the old paper and cloth bindings. The color palette is composed of deep earthy browns, warm tans, and muted olives, evoking a sense of cozy intellectualism and classic elegance." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAG6gAnVbSR3kzxclPXxESl4VW0n8BrWyZjzzvlVR1A60knZgc5ghpWT6UxJft-8qpX-puqdBAv2RqICLxtCTVIV_Y2O6bfkz17FmpXaITdbIXRWUUnEqukw4NymxMrxQpJcGEd_xscHQYTcdAY_Ax45R4j8gjYrbxbOxifHkHKKXMxbuerau-Q0ef7X60CVIraVAH72rsaverjyqgSSGB5lNRgKCfdRv2-iog_tFDG6xngeJqI8txJytrOAzamZm6efrREi0SJbn0">
</div>
<div class="flex-1">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-lg">Gợi ý nhập hàng tuần này</h3>
<p class="text-body-md opacity-90 mt-1">Dựa trên dữ liệu bán hàng, các đầu sách thể loại "Kinh điển" đang có xu hướng hết hàng sớm trong 5 ngày tới. Hãy cân nhắc lập phiếu nhập mới cho nhà cung cấp NXB Trẻ.</p>
<button class="mt-4 text-on-primary-container font-label-md border-b border-on-primary-container/30 hover:border-on-primary-container transition-all">Xem danh sách gợi ý</button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Footer Section -->
<footer class="w-full py-12 px-margin-desktop bg-surface-container-highest border-t border-outline-variant mt-12">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
<div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1">
<span class="font-display-lg text-headline-md text-primary">The Open Folio</span>
<p class="text-caption text-on-surface-variant mt-4">Hệ thống quản lý thư viện hiện đại, kết nối tri thức và độc giả thông qua trải nghiệm tối giản và chuyên nghiệp.</p>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-label-md text-primary mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">Hệ thống</h4>
<ul class="space-y-2 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
